data.title: Oh Brian's On The Green
data.meta_description: Oh Brian's on the Green, is a Gastropub experience designed to provide friends and families a place to appreciate exceptional culinary experiences in an exciting social venue. Through expertly prepared casual fare, fine dining entrées, and chef-driven seasonal daily specials, Oh'Brian's on the Green shares its passion for great food, from the traditional to the adventurous. Choose to be seated in our pub area for a more casual environment or dine in our newly renovated dining room. If outdoor dining is your thing, our outdoor patio provides a scenic view of the Hyatt Hills Golf Course. We look forward to serving you!
data.text:
Book your next party with us!

Come to celebrate your special event or - give us the opportunity to make your event memorable. We look forward to serving and seeing you soon!

Let us cater your next event

Oh Brian's On The Green would be honored to provide our services for your next event. Each event is bespoke to your tastes and needs, to provide the best experience possible for you and your guests.

Established in 2013.

Oh Brian's on the Green, is a Gastropub experience designed to provide friends and families a place to appreciate exceptional culinary experiences in an exciting social venue. Through expertly prepared casual fare, fine dining entrées, and chef-driven seasonal daily specials, Oh'Brian's on the Green shares its passion for great food, from the traditional to the adventurous. Choose to be seated in our pub area for a more casual environment or dine in our newly renovated dining room. If outdoor dining is your thing, our outdoor patio provides a scenic view of the Hyatt Hills Golf Course. We look forward to serving you!
